  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\"><img alt=\"House Frey.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/50px-House_Frey.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/75px-House_Frey.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/100px-House_Frey.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Maester</span><br />Willamen</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Maesters\" title=\"Maesters\"><img alt=\"Maester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/50px-Maester.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/75px-Maester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/100px-Maester.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Willamen_Frey_by_Lopata_4.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Willamen Frey by Lopata 4.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/4b/Willamen_Frey_by_Lopata_4.jpg/350px-Willamen_Frey_by_Lopata_4.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"439\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/4b/Willamen_Frey_by_Lopata_4.jpg/525px-Willamen_Frey_by_Lopata_4.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/4b/Willamen_Frey_by_Lopata_4.jpg/700px-Willamen_Frey_by_Lopata_4.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Willamen by Lopata 4</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nWillamen Frey</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">Maester</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/Longbow_Hall\" title=\"Longbow Hall\">Longbow Hall</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\">House Frey</a></li><li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">Citadel</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hunter\" title=\"House Hunter\">House Hunter</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rivermen\" title=\"Rivermen\">Rivermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_272_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">272</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/280_AC\" title=\"280 AC\">280&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">Walder Frey</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Mother</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Bethany_Rosby\" title=\"Bethany Rosby\">Bethany Rosby</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appendix)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Willamen</b>, born <b>Willamen Frey</b>, is a <a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">maester</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">Citadel</a> in service at <a href=\"/index.php/Longbow_Hall\" title=\"Longbow Hall\">Longbow Hall</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hunter\" title=\"House Hunter\">House Hunter</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> He is the seventeenth son of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">Walder Frey</a> and the third son born in the marriage between Walder and <a href=\"/index.php/Bethany_Rosby\" title=\"Bethany Rosby\">Bethany Rosby</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Willamen_Frey&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Willamen took his <a href=\"/index.php/Maesters#Maester.27s_vows\" title=\"Maesters\">maester's vows</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/298_AC\" title=\"298 AC\">298&#160;AC</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Willamen_Frey&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; hei